  "description": "<p>\n\t在四级考试中，阅读分值占35%，如果你的薄弱点在于阅读，那么集中精力攻一攻阅读，对你的分数提高是极有好处的。今天小编就来给大家系统性地讲一讲如何系统复习阅读，提高阅读分数。</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166406101433/\" target=\"_blank\">本文已录入四六级备考攻略&gt;&gt;戳我去看更多专项复习攻略</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/13c83c3ab96947729d71fe453715da0f.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>▼考纲解读</strong>：阅读理解部分考核学生通过阅读获取书面信息的能力，包括理解主旨大意、重要事实和细节、隐含意义，判断作者的观点、态度等。</p>\n<p>\n\t要攻下阅读，切不可心急，一上来就一整篇一整篇文章地练习，很容易就产生疲倦之感。所以首先也要做热身练习。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>【阅读任务一】背高频词汇；学阅读技巧</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t阅读的提高，绝非一蹴而就，熟知高频词能帮助你扫除阅读障碍，学会分析长难句有助于更好地理解文章，学会阅读技巧则能帮助你在考试有限的时间内快速做题。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>※阅读高频词社刊：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/mag/165486291161/\" target=\"_blank\">四级阅读高频词汇</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">※精华文章： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p729817/\" target=\"_blank\">三招教你攻克四级阅读</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p471279/\" target=\"_blank\">如何抓住英语四级阅读的主题思想</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p751872/\" target=\"_blank\">四级阅读：排除选项四大原则</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p750005/\"